    </a>
</div>
<div class="credit-caption">
    <div class="caption-wrap">
        <div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption">
        </div>


    </div>

</div>
</div>


    <div id="res152259514" class="bucketwrap bookedition">
      <h6><a href="https://www.npr.org/books/titles/152259496/a-rich-spot-of-earth-thomas-jeffersons-revolutionary-garden-at-monticello">A Rich Spot of Earth</a></h6>
   <p>Thomas Jefferson's Revolutionary Garden at Monticello</p>   <p class="author">by <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/152259501/peter-j-hatch"><span>Peter J. Hatch</span></a></p>   <div class="bookinfo">
            <p>Hardcover, 263 pages <span class="pipe">|</span></p>      <a href="#" class="purchase" data-metrics='{"category":"Ecommerce","action":"Click purchase book"}' >purchase</a>      <div class="ecommercepop">
